        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Disaster Relief Transparency Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development and the Federal Emergency Management Agency to report on the allocation and applicant approval rates of specified assistance programs related to disaster recovery. </p>]]>
        </text>
